So, that's the way it was.

1339
01:38:52,510 --> 01:38:54,053
Yeah.

1340
01:38:55,304 --> 01:38:59,307
When you first got here, you had
the right to go back for one day,

1341
01:38:59,308 --> 01:39:00,684
and you didn't.

