see her from here?

1386
01:41:29,083 --> 01:41:31,536
Sure, you can, if you want to.

1387
01:41:34,338 --> 01:41:38,091
Nah. If she ain't happy,
I don't wanna look.

1388
01:41:38,092 --> 01:41:42,012
Well, right now, she appears
to be having a fine time.

1389
01:41:42,013 --> 01:41:45,473
